title: Vegetarian lasagne
details: A dinner staple in most Aussie households, lasagne has a history of being a go-to meal that will leave the whole family satisfied.

title: Affair With Pizza
details: Pizza is one of the most popular foods on the planet, and particularly here in the USA. Americans eat 3 billion fresh and a billion frozen pizzas every single year. That’s an avertotal_view of 23 pounds of pizza per person!

title: Healthy quiche
details: t’s officially 2023, which means those ‘eating clean’ new years resolutions are in full swing. Whether it’s eating more veggies, cutting down on processed foods, or simply wanting to live a healthier lifestyle, many Aussies (us included) are officially on the hunt for new and yummy better-for-you recipes to set the tone for the new year.
